\end_inset

 below.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
The floppy drive (and hard drive partitions) under DOS.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
LDBS: A disc image format still under development.
 See LDBS/ldbs.html for more information.
\end_layout

